What I think it should be in fix.100:
10.000        'ADEP(1)'   # 10 soil layers 1, 2, 3  -- these should add up to 240 cm, following example in COLO STATE manual
20.000        'ADEP(2)'   # 20 soil layers 4 ,5 -- as explained, these are to map Daycent soil layers to the old Century model
15.000        'ADEP(3)'   # 40 layer 6 -- which is still part of the codebase. See fig 2.
